---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Disability Insurance | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Disability insurance provides a monthly benefit if you cannot work due to illness or injury. Contact Heidi Blondin to explore disability and income-protection strategies."
>

  <section class="bg-brand-plum py-20">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow-light mb-5">Insurance</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-white text-balance" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Disability Insurance</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>Many Canadians protect their risk of dying with life insurance. But what would happen if you were in a severe car accident and couldn't work? How long could you survive before you had to dip into your retirement savings or sell your home?</p>
        <p>For a 30 year old female the risk of becoming disabled before the age of 65 is almost 43%. The same risk for a male is 37%. You can't predict the future but you can protect it with Disability Insurance (according to statistics provided by Manulife Insurance).</p>
        <p>If you are unable to work, a disability plan can provide a monthly benefit to help cover your living expenses. Contact Heidi to explore Disability Insurance and other income-protection strategies.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Request A Quote For Disability Insurance Today</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
